(202, 1, '2013-11-12 14:46:38', '2013-11-12 14:46:38', 'Congratulation!!! Selamat untuk siswa-siswi piano Bina Seni Suara karena SEMUA berhasil LULUS dalam ujian ROYAL - ABRSM (Associated Board Of Royal Schools Of Music). Akhirnya para instruktur bisa bernafas lega, melihat hasil kerja kerasnya selama kurang lebih 6 bulan tidaklah sia-sia. Semoga dengan hasil ini, tambah memicu siswa agar ditahun berikutnya akan lebih bersemangat dan lebih berprestasi....SEMOGA......\r\n<p style="text-align: center;"><strong>DAFTAR SISWA LULUS UJIAN PIANO ROYAL _ABRSM</strong>\r\n<strong> HOTEL INTERCONTINENTAL MIDPLAZA JAKARTA - 12 SEPTEMBER 2013</strong></p>\r\n\r\n<table class=" aligncenter" width="100%" border="1" cellspacing="0" cellpadding="0">\r\n<tbody>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td valign="bottom" nowrap="nowrap" width="29"><b>NO</b></td>\r\n<td valign="bottom" nowrap="nowrap" width="272"><b>NAME</b></td>\r\n<td valign="bottom" nowrap="nowrap" width="85"><b>GRADE</b></td>\r\n<td valign="bottom" nowrap="nowrap" width="85"><b>MARK</b></td>\r\n<td valign="bottom" nowrap="nowrap" width="85"><b>PASS</b></td>\r\n</tr>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td valign="bottom" nowrap="nowrap" width="29">1</td>\r\n<td valign="bottom" nowrap="nowrap" width="272">Cut Nyak Farisa Nuzulya Machmud</td>\r\n<td valign="bottom" nowrap="nowrap" width="85">III</td>\r\n<td valign="bottom" nowrap="nowrap" width="85">134</td>\r\n<td valign="bottom" nowrap="nowrap" width="85">D</td>\r\n</tr>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td valign="bottom" nowrap="nowrap" width="29">2</td>\r\n<td valign="bottom" nowrap="nowrap" width="272">Apsari Shanti Nayoan</td>\r\n<td valign="bottom" nowrap="nowrap" width="85">III</td>\r\n<td valign="bottom" nowrap="nowrap" width="85">138</td>\r\n<td valign="bottom" nowrap="nowrap" width="85">D</td>\r\n</tr>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td valign="bottom" nowrap="nowrap" width="29">3</td>\r\n<td valign="bottom" nowrap="nowrap" width="272">Julia Tsara Dhuha</td>\r\n<td valign="bottom" nowrap="nowrap" width="85">III</td>\r\n<td valign="bottom" nowrap="n